response.overview: June 7th, 2008 :: Ring Of Honor presents Respect Is Earned 2. The event took place on June 7th from the Pennsylvania National Guard Armory in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania and aired on August 1st. Matches include:  • Falls Count Anywhere Match Necro Butcher vs Jay Briscoe  • ROH World Tag Team Championship Match The Age of the Fall (c) vs Austin Aries & Bryan Danielsoni  • ROH World Championship Nigel McGuinness (c) vs Go Shiozak  • Fight Without Honor Roderick Strong vs Erick Stevens  • Davey Richards vs Claudio Castagnoli  • Sweet & Sour Inc. (Chris Hero, Adam Pearce & Shane Hagadorn) vs Brent Albright, Delirious & Pelle Primeau  • Jigsaw vs Eddie Kingston  • Kevin Steen & El Generico vs The Vulture Squad
response.title: ROH: Respect Is Earned II
